text: "Mustang Sally" is a 1966 song by Wilson Pickett and taken from his album The Wicked Pickett. It went to number 23 in the United States, number 4 in Canada and number 28 in the United Kingdom. It was used in the 1991 movie The Commitments and went to number 17 in New Zealand.
